It claims to be ultra-silky with a weightless texture and it also should ... also don't see a plumping effect. Matte lipsticks usually tend to be a little bit drying, but the lipstick from Kiko isn't as drying as matte lipsticks from other brands.This lipstick shade looks very natural and it's a pinkish nude shade. ... colors- Long lasting- Packaging- Affordable (6 - 7 €)- Texture- Hypoallergenic- Won't smudgeContra- Not very moisturizing- No plumping effectWhere to buy?The Kiko Velvet Mat Satin Lipstick is available at your local Kiko store or on their website.

Nail Polish Battle: Kiko 295 vs. Zoya Robyn vs. Essie Strut Your Stuff I have another Nail Polish Battle for you guys today, this time with three vivid cerulean blues. The battle polishes are Kiko number 295 called Cerulean Blue, Zoya Robyn and Essie Strut Your Stuff. These all look pretty similar in the bottle, ... coats. They are all pretty easy to apply, thought they were all just slightly runny but nothing too major.Essie and Kiko seem pretty much dupes, though I'd say Essie's color is slightly brighter whereas Kiko is a tad darker. Zoya is the one that's most different from the other two, eventhough it's also really bright ... between these three, so if you have one, I don't think you need the others. For me from these three Kiko and Zoya were easiest to apply since the Essie has that thin brush that I'm not too fond of. I ... the fact that Essie seemed to stain my skin and cuticles just slightly when I removed it whereas Zoya or Kiko didn't. They are all quite pigmented, so you need to keep that in mind and maybe use two coats of base coat under these all.Kiko was my bf's pick for me from all the Kiko polishes from Ancona's Kiko selection, so it's a bit more special to me than the other two. I'm also drawn to that little bit ... doing my decision based on that.Final verdict: This time Essie has to go as I want to keep that special Kiko and that dusty Zoya.Which one is your favorite?

• Gorgeous mauvish pink shade.

Cons of KIKO Ultra Glossy Stylo SPF 15 Lipstick in #815 Rhododendron Pink:

KIKO Colour Sphere Eyeshadow #33 Burnt Umber Review Hello beautiful ladies!
Today’s review will be on the third eyeshadow #33 Burnt Umber from the Colour Sphere range of KIKO. I have already reviewed #40 Gray Multicolor and #35 Malachite Green. The review is pretty much the same when it ... mentioned on the website it is nowhere to be seen on the eyeshadow pot or the carton.

My Experience with KIKO Colour Sphere Eyeshadow #33 Burnt Umber:
Burnt Umber is a pretty combination of burnt brown with a slight purple tint ... It does not seem waterproof, but needs an eye makeup remover to remove all the color and sparkle.

Pros of KIKO Colour Sphere Eyeshadow #33 Burnt Umber:
• Burnt brown with purple tint.
• Silver sparkle.
• Shimmery, silky radiant finish. ... Easy to blend.
• Good pigmentation.
• Staying power is good.
• Travel friendly.
• Does not crease.
Cons of KIKO Colour Sphere Eyeshadow #33 Burnt Umber:
• A little fallout.
• Not waterproof.
• Availability in India.
IMBB Rating: Would rate this 4.8/5.
Would I Recommend KIKO Colour Sphere Eyeshadow #33 Burnt Umber: Yes, for sure.
Would I Repurchase KIKO Colour Sphere Eyeshadow #33 Burnt Umber: I would love to try their other shades as I would not be able to finish this one anytime sooner.

Kiko #35 Malachite Green Colour Sphere Eyeshadow Review Hello beautiful ladies
I am still not done reviewing my Kiko and Zoeva stuff completely, but then I thought I should jumble between the products at least so you my lovely ... bored of it. So, after reviewing #40 Gray Multicolor Colour, today I bring to you all the second shade from Kiko’s Colour Sphere range, #35 Malachite Green.

Claims:
Baked silk effect eyeshadow, brilliant and easy to blend. Rich in illuminating pigments ... intense. Well tolerated by sensitive eyes. Available in 36 colour varieties.

Price:
GBP 4.10
Ingredients:

Quantity:
1.8g
My Experience with Kiko #35 Malachite Green Colour Sphere Eyeshadow:
The eyeshadow comes in a small round pan which has a see through lid ... It does not seem waterproof, but needs an eye makeup remover to remove all the color and sparkle.

Pros of Kiko #35 Malachite Green Colour Sphere Eyeshadow:

Pretty bluish green shade.
Silver sparkle.
Shimmery, silky and radiant finish.
Smooth texture.
Easy to blend.
Good pigmentation.
Staying power is good.
Travel friendly.
Does not crease.

Cons of Kiko #35 Malachite Green Colour Sphere Eyeshadow:

A little fallout.
Not Waterproof.
Availability in India.

Would I Recommend Kiko #35 Malachite Green Colour Sphere Eyeshadow?
Yes, for sure.
Would I Repurchase Kiko #35 Malachite Green Colour Sphere Eyeshadow?
I would love try their other shades, as I would not be able to finish this one anytime sooner.
IMBB Rating:
4.8/5.

Ho deciso inolte di mostrarvi uno swatch comparativo del rossetto Kiko e del celeberrimo Instigator di Mac. Se sul mio braccio c'è un minimo di differenza sulle labbra il colore è ... Considerate che eventuali micro differenze sono dovute alla luce pessima che io avevo in casa quel giorno.  Essendo quello di Kiko veramente di qualità vi consiglio di acquistarlo se eravate interessate ad Instigator. Kiko economicamente è più accessibile ed è diffusa in maniera capillare in tutta Italia, dal nord al sud.

Kiko Margarita Dreams Milano Deco Delight Lipstick Review Hello all,
After reviewing the shade “Tropical Juice,” I am back with the review of another shade from Kiko Milano Deco Delight Lipstick – Margarita Dreams. Read on to find out more about this lipstick.

Price:
$10
Product Description: ... decorated in the “Miami Beach Babe” style. Gently fragranced with a vanilla aroma. Available in six colors.

Ingredients:

My Experience with Kiko Margarita Dreams Milano Deco Delight Lipstick:
Packaging: The lipstick comes in a cute purple polka dotted case. The cap clicks ... lipsticks will enjoy wearing this. Since this is such a sheer shade, it will look good on all skin tones.  Kiko says that the color is buildable, but I did not find so.

Texture/Finish/Lasting Power:  The lipstick is very creamy and ... the formula and pigmentation of the lipstick is just okay but it is the packaging which steals the show.
Pros of Kiko Margarita Dreams Milano Deco Delight Lipstick:

Adorable and unique packaging and lipstick bullet.
Beautiful pink shade.
Glides smoothly on the lips.
Keeps the lips hydrated for a long time.
Nice glossy finish.

Cons of Kiko Margarita Dreams Milano Deco Delight Lipstick:

Sheer pigmentation.
Color is not buildable as claimed.
Poor staying power.
Very creamy and likely to melt in hot conditions.

IMBB Rating:
3.5/5
Would I Repurchase/Recommend Kiko Margarita Dreams Milano Deco Delight Lipstick?
If like me, you get swayed by everything cute, you will love this lipstick.  I already own one more shade from the range and would not buy more.

Available in 6 shades.KIKO Cool Touch Eyeshadow (£8.90) This is an absolute lovely texture ; a hybrid powder/cream that has a spongey like texture. Available in 8 shades.KIKO Glassy Lipgloss (£7.90)This is probably my favourite product from the range and I'm  a little bit in love. 3.5g
Claims:
Creamy lipstick with pure, intense colour and exclusive design. A ... lipstick. The name is mentioned on the website but not on the carton or the lipstick itself.
My Experience with KIKO Luscious Cream Lipstick #504 Raspberry:

Raspberry is nowhere close to its name. Reading the name, one might think it is ... a brick red brown. Say brick like brown with slight reddish tint. These lipsticks belong to the creamy range from KIKO. Although there are no shimmers in it and it has no shine or glossiness, the finish is not outright flat ... when you don’t want to have bright lips around, this one surely makes a good choice.

FOTD:

• Dreamy, buttery texture
• No tugging ... shape of the bullet helps in better application
• Good pigmentation
• Good staying power
• Travel friendly
Cons of KIKO Luscious Cream Lipstick #504 Raspberry:
• Transfers a bit to cutlery
• Not waterproof
• Availability in India
Would I Recommend KIKO Luscious Cream Lipstick #504 Raspberry?
Yes definitely.
Would I repurchase KIKO Luscious Cream Lipstick #504 Raspberry?
Yes sure

〜やり方〜
1親指と小指にくすみグリーンをベタ塗り、人差し指はパールピンクをベタ塗り、小指には根元の方にラインシールを貼ります。
2中指はネイビーのハーフフレンチを施した後、ダイソーの立体ネイルシールを配置します。
3薬指はducateのコンデンスミルクをのせた後、乾かないうちにくすみグリーンをちょんちょんのせて、コンデンスミルクのハケでぼかします。そのうえから金箔をのせます。
4各爪にトップコートを2.3回重ねます。

Trucco autunno 2017: a Venezia con la nuova collezione make-up di KIKO MILANO Come si fa a concentrare l’essenza romantica, misteriosa e seducente di Venezia in una collezione di make-up? Kiko Milano lo ha fatto chiamando Ross Lovegrove, designer futurista di fama internazionale e coinvolgendo 11 influencer internazionali.
Per creare il ... scelto il blu profondo e ha creato pezzi unici, eleganti e preziosi che concentrano quella che lui stesso definisce la KIKONESS: «Un insieme di eleganza, sensualità, femminilità, spigliatezza e praticità».
Con le 11 influencer internazionali KIKO Milano ha invece fatto tappa nell’incantevole Venezia. Per loro ha messo a disposizione make-up e hairstyle in accordo con il ... acque in un romantico giro in gondola e hanno degustato i sapori tipici della tradizione veneziana.
Le influencer scelte da KIKO sono: Valentina Vignali, Giulia Latini e Diletta Amenta dall’Italia, Silvia Rodriguez Bernal dalla Spagna, Marta Melro dal Portogallo, Anna Jansen, ... Sheida Barbareza e Renee Farah dal Medio Oriente.
L'articolo Trucco autunno 2017: a Venezia con la nuova collezione make-up di KIKO MILANO sembra essere il primo su Vogue.it.

🇬🇧 I ordered a big box full of make up from @kikomilano this week and this is the first beauty, face palette. 🎀
It has a bronzer, a blush and a highlighter. Great for little trips. 🇹🇷Selam kizlar! Gecenlerde @kikomilanoturkey dan buyuk bir alisveris yaptim, bir suru indirimde sey vardi. 😈 Bu yuz paletine de bi sans verdim, mini seyahatlar icin cok iyi bence. Parmakli resimler gelsin mi ne dersiniz? 😏💗 #nurselsblog Tagged: @kikomilano, @kikomilanoturkey

🇬🇧The Hero of my make up of the day. It’s the Radiant Fusion Baked Powder by @kikomilano . It really leaves the skin like velvet and great for setting the foundation.
🇹🇷Bugunku makyajimin bgubku kahramini @kikomilanoturkey nun bu guzel Radiant Fusion Baked pudrasi. Gercekten yuzu kadife gibi birakiyor ve makyaji sabitlemede oldukca basarili. Bayildim, indirimdeydi kizlae kosun alin. Ayrica ambalaji da muhtesem. 🎀 #nurselsblog Tagged: @kikomilano, @kikomilanoturkey

🇬🇧I was a bit judgemental against the cushion foundations but this one is really great by @kikomilano . It looks really natural and quite thin, but has medium coverage. Especially it’s on sale right now. Have a look girls. 🖤
🇹🇷Yine bir @kikomilanoturkey urunuyle geldim kizlar! Bu sekildeki cushion fondotenlere karsi onyargiliydim ama bunu kullandiktan sonra bayildim! Gercekten cantaya at cik bir urun, ... rengim Natural Glow 30 ve cildime tam uydu. Degisik alttonlari var kesinlikle cok memnun kalicaginiza eminim. Indirimdeyken kosun. 🖤 Tagged: @kikomilano, @kikomilanoturkey

KIKO FULL COVERAGE 2 IN 1: FONDOTINTA AD ALTA COPRENZA
Uno dei primi fondotinta di cui vi voglio parlare è una novità in casa Kiko Milano. Il loro nuovo fondotinta super coprente unisce due azioni in un unico prodotto.

L’idea di Kiko è quella di lanciare sul mercato un prodotto che crei un’ottima base viso e allo stesso tempo cancelli e minimizzi le imperfezioni e discromie.

Kiko, Full Coverage 2 in 1 Fonudation & Concealer. Prezzo: 18,95 € su kikocosmetics.it
Il particolare applicatore ricorda quello dei correttori liquidi, e infatti il prodotto offre  una formula a doppia azione che permette ... di ottenere un risultato finale personalizzato e modulabile.

ottima copertura e tante nuance tra cui scegliere per il fondotinta di kiko

La mia guida ai saldi Kiko: cosa comprare... e cosa evitare! Bellezze, finalmente sono arrivati i SALDI! Vi anticipo già che abbiamo in programma diversi articoli succulenti per voi, e oggi iniziamo con uno dei brand che più fanno gola in questo periodo.
Kiko infatti mette in offerta le edizioni limitate della stagione precedente, che in alcuni casi sono dei veri gioiellini a livello ... avrete già qualche idea!
In ogni caso, credo che possa esservi utile un riassunto generale su quali sono i prodotti Kiko da non farsi assolutamente scappare ai saldi, ma non solo! Ho aggiunto anche quelli che potrebbero tentarvi avendo ora un ... Vi ho detto tutto , è il momento di lasciarvi al post!


LA COLLEZIONE ARCTIC HOLIDAY
Una delle edizioni limitate Kiko che ci ha dato più soddisfazioni questo inverno è stata la Arctic Holiday, ricca di prodotti favolosi!

Arctic Holiday Holographic Highlighter. Prezzo in offerta: 8,35€ su kikocosmetics.com
Partiamo da un illuminante che  l’ideale se volete provare l’effetto olografico senza spendere tanto. Soprattutto se bagnato, ha ottime pigmentazione e sfumabilità, e una durata impeccabile dalla mattina alla sera.

Arctic Holiday Volume Mascara. Prezzo in offerta: 7,65€ su kikocosmetics.com
Questo mascara non è super volumizzante, ma riesce ad allungare bene le ciglia e a mantenere la piega. Ha un colore molto intenso e contiene fibre sintetiche.


Arctic Holiday Matte lipstick. Prezzo in offerta: 7,65€ su kikocosmetics.com
Se i rossetti matte per voi non sono mai troppi, o desiderate qualche nuovo colore, potete curiosare tra questi, che sono confortevoli, durano a lungo e non sbavano.
